{"tid":2410083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【母愛】新研究：母親即使確診母乳不僅零病毒 還傳武肺抗體給寶寶","createTime":"2021-02-16T10:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T10:47:17.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9726f3631b82aa8e5233839c457c8a42f90eb52b","tid":2410083,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/16/phppDLsfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2FphppDLsfG.jpg&h=7b9742e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2021/02/16 15:12<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）全球大流行，確診染疫的媽媽是否應與寶寶隔離屢引熱議，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">最新研究顯示，母親並不會透過乳汁傳播武肺病毒給新生兒，相反的，還會輸送能「中和」該病毒的抗體給寶寶。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，最近發表在美國微生物學會期刊《mBio》的報告中，美國愛達荷大學的研究人員針對18名確診武肺的媽媽與其母乳樣本進行分析，發現所有樣本均不含武肺病毒，其中將近3分之2具有2種對該疾病特異的抗體。<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，即使母親感染武漢肺炎，母乳餵養對嬰兒也是相當安全的，甚至對孩子有所助益。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組目前正準備把相關研究擴大至50名確診女性，並將在未來幾個月內繼續追蹤進展，以適時更新對民眾發布之醫學建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440597&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=ba4dcd7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440597&h=f0f3ca3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440597</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">很想要吧！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">(以下圖片只供參考 與新聞內容無關)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.juksy.com/files/articles/95839/800x_100_w-5dbfd0e594b08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F95839%2F800x_100_w-5dbfd0e594b08.jpg&h=70a73f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2020/03/29/phpJffGcl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F03%2F29%2FphpJffGcl.jpg&h=b0404336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2617/2617024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2617%2F2617024.jpg&h=37155526&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58f79f59eb5718caf75b49ba446581a949e0020f","tid":2410083,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"想drink人奶了"},{"pid":"e6b61b171cee12bb299ce1abac5286c462343914","tid":2410083,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"預防武肺<br />\n及早飲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db6812ba9ed155a80125c2488b162b94b414edb","tid":2410083,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"武肺奶媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53bc49f5f1a18fb16342cf22f0e9c5ebe7ddb4a","tid":2410083,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBzajBC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBzajBC.gif&h=b927ddb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76f3d67b66dbbd4b02ef8d3f5a114cd1090226ec","tid":2410083,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"個BB奶咗嘢唔通又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580695efdbbd6b325aabba9eef0a634a4b1d3f00","tid":2410083,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac